sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.Datapac.description: The label for category Datapack Customization in sidebar tutorialSidebar

sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.Datapac.message:
By browsing game directories, you might find data files in `.../<GameDir>/config/croparia/data/...`.
This is where Croparia IF automize the data insertion, and you are **NOT SUGGESTED** to modify any data inside.
Because Croparia IF will try to override all these files by default, which means any changes you've made here might be lost.

However, it is pretty fine if you just want to see the definition of the data files (i.e. you are in "read-only" mode).

sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.Resourc.message:
By browsing game directories, you might find resource files in `.../<GameDir>/config/croparia/assets/...`.
This is where Croparia IF automize the resource insertion, and you are **NOT SUGGESTED** to modify any data inside.
Because Croparia IF will try to override all these files by default, which means any changes you've made here might be lost.

However, it is pretty fine if you just want to see the definition of the data files (i.e. you are in "read-only" mode).
